{
  "id": "69c3448468ab78e7b72df396",
  "title": "世界中の金の総量",
  "created": 1774404742,
  "updated": 1774409446,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69c3448468ab78e7b72df396",
      "text": "世界中の金の総量",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774404742,
      "updated": 1774404742
    },
    {
      "id": "69c34486000000000043bf84",
      "text": "意外と少なかったはず[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774404742,
      "updated": 1774404750
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3448e000000000043bf86",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774404750,
      "updated": 1774404750
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3448e000000000043bf87",
      "text": "> イギリスの貴金属調査会社トムソン・ロイターGFMSの統計によれば、2014年末時点で総量は 183,600トンである（金の地上在庫とはこれまでに採掘され精製加工された金の総量のこと）。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774404751,
      "updated": 1774409197
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3448d000000000043bf85",
      "text": "> [https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/金#金の地上在庫 金#金の地上在庫]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774404750,
      "updated": 1774404879
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3453b0000000000021fb9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774404923,
      "updated": 1774404923
    },
    {
      "id": "69c345010000000000021fb7",
      "text": "ついでに",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774404865,
      "updated": 1774404923
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3453c0000000000021fba",
      "text": " （参考）主要各国の保有量",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774404925,
      "updated": 1774404938
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3453d0000000000021fbb",
      "text": "  [アメリカ国旗.icon]\tアメリカ：\t8,134トン\t（外貨準備に占める割合は78.2 %）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774404926,
      "updated": 1774409202
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3453d0000000000021fbc",
      "text": "  [ドイツ国旗.icon]\tドイツ：\t3,413トン\t（同66.3 %）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774404926,
      "updated": 1774409205
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3453d0000000000021fbd",
      "text": "  [フランス国旗.icon]\tフランス：\t2,541トン\t（同59.4 %）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774404926,
      "updated": 1774409207
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3453d0000000000021fbe",
      "text": "  [イタリア国旗.icon]\tイタリア：\t2,452トン\t（同68.1 %）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774404926,
      "updated": 1774409209
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3453d0000000000021fbf",
      "text": "  [スイス国旗.icon]　　\tスイス：\t1,064トン\t（同39.8 %）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774404926,
      "updated": 1774409211
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3453d0000000000021fc0",
      "text": "  [日本国旗.icon]\t日本：　　\t765トン \t（同2.1 %）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774404926,
      "updated": 1774409216
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3453d0000000000021fc1",
      "text": "  [オランダ国旗.icon]:\tオランダ：\t621トン \t（同61.2 %）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774404926,
      "updated": 1774405671
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3453d0000000000021fc2",
      "text": "  [中華人民共和国旗.icon]:\t中国：　　\t600トン \t（同1 %）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774404926,
      "updated": 1774405673
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3453d0000000000021fc3",
      "text": "  [インド国旗.icon]:\tインド：\t358トン \t（同3.3 %）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774404926,
      "updated": 1774405675
    },
    {
      "id": "69c355c000000000001a2708",
      "text": " このリストの合計は 19,848 トン",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774409153,
      "updated": 1774409193
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3567900000000001a2709",
      "text": " \t全体に対する割合は 10.81%",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774409338,
      "updated": 1774409411
    },
    {
      "id": "69c345040000000000021fb8",
      "text": "\t金保有量が多いのに外貨準備に占める割合が小さい日本と、金保有量が少ないのに外貨準備に占める割合が大きいオランダの違いが面白い[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774404868,
      "updated": 1774409153
    },
    {
      "id": "69c345010000000000021fb6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774404865,
      "updated": 1774404865
    },
    {
      "id": "69c34da300000000001a26e8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774407076,
      "updated": 1774407076
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3519300000000001a26f8",
      "text": "[*** 時価総額（？）]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774408084,
      "updated": 1774408109
    },
    {
      "id": "69c34da300000000001a26e9",
      "text": " 全体の量（183,600トン）をグラムに直して、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774407076,
      "updated": 1774409225
    },
    {
      "id": "69c34dac00000000001a26eb",
      "text": " \t183,600,000,000[$ \\lbrack \\rm g\\rbrack]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774407085,
      "updated": 1774409230
    },
    {
      "id": "69c34dac00000000001a26ea",
      "text": " 相場（2026/03/25 現在は大体 2 万円/g）をかけると金の時価総額（？）が出せるはず",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774407084,
      "updated": 1774408090
    },
    {
      "id": "69c34dda00000000001a26ed",
      "text": " \t3,672 兆円",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774407131,
      "updated": 1774409234
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3503700000000001a26f1",
      "text": " 計算上の桁数が気になるが、変動が大きいので有効数字とかいうレベルの話ではない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774407736,
      "updated": 1774408090
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3504900000000001a26f2",
      "text": " \t価格が倍近く変動する上に全体の量は増えていく。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774407754,
      "updated": 1774408090
    },
    {
      "id": "69c34dcc00000000001a26ec",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774407116,
      "updated": 1774407116
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3505600000000001a26f3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774407767,
      "updated": 1774407767
    },
    {
      "id": "69c34ee800000000001a26ee",
      "text": " ちなみに：世界の株式時価総額は 150 兆ドルらしい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774407400,
      "updated": 1774408090
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3507f00000000001a26f4",
      "text": " \t158円/ドルで円に直すと大体 2.37 京円",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774407808,
      "updated": 1774408090
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3515400000000001a26f7",
      "text": " \t金の時価総額（？）の 6.45 倍",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774408020,
      "updated": 1774408090
    },
    {
      "id": "69c354ae00000000001a2706",
      "text": "  \tこの数値は何を意味するのだろう。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774408879,
      "updated": 1774408928
    },
    {
      "id": "69c354df00000000001a2707",
      "text": "  \t金本位制との解離度のように扱えないだろうか。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774408928,
      "updated": 1774408928
    },
    {
      "id": "69c34eec00000000001a26ef",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774407405,
      "updated": 1774407405
    },
    {
      "id": "69c351af00000000001a26fb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774408112,
      "updated": 1774408112
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3519b00000000001a26f9",
      "text": "[*** 体積]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774408092,
      "updated": 1774408122
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3523f00000000001a26fe",
      "text": " 全体の量（183,600トン）をグラムに直して、",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774408255,
      "updated": 1774409259
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3523f00000000001a26ff",
      "text": " \t183,600,000,000[$ \\lbrack \\rm g\\rbrack]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774408255,
      "updated": 1774409258
    },
    {
      "id": "69c351ba00000000001a26fc",
      "text": "\t密度は[$ 19.32\\ \\lbrack\\rm g/cm^3\\rbrack]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774408123,
      "updated": 1774408344
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3524100000000001a2701",
      "text": " 体積は[$ 9.503\\times10^9\\ \\lbrack\\rm cm^3\\rbrack=9.503\\times10^3\\ \\lbrack\\rm m^3\\rbrack]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774408258,
      "updated": 1774408482
    },
    {
      "id": "69c353f500000000001a2703",
      "text": " 三乗根を取ると、同じ体積を持つ立方体の一辺の長さが出る。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774408694,
      "updated": 1774408727
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3541700000000001a2704",
      "text": "  [$ 21.18\\ \\lbrack\\rm m\\rbrack]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774408727,
      "updated": 1774408759
    },
    {
      "id": "69c3545000000000001a2705",
      "text": "  昔聞いた話（世界中の金を集めると大体各辺が 23m の立方体になる）と同じくらいなので合ってそう。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774408785,
      "updated": 1774409446
    },
    {
      "id": "69c352d900000000001a2702",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1774408409,
      "updated": 1774408409
    }
  ]
}